  ;; --- TEXT ANNOTATIONS (component placement guide) ---
  (text "=== LOWER PCB COMPONENT PLACEMENT ===\n\nU1: ESP32-S3-WROOM-1 â€” Center-right of board\n     GPIO1â†’JOY_X, GPIO2â†’JOY_Y, GPIO3â†’JOY_SW\n     GPIO4â†’VBAT_SENSE, GPIO5â†’BTN_LEFT\n     GPIO6â†’BTN_RIGHT, GPIO7â†’BTN_BACK, GPIO8â†’BTN_FWD\n     GPIO19â†’USB_DN, GPIO20â†’USB_DP\n     3V3â†’3V3, GNDâ†’GND\n\nU2: TP4056 (SOP-8) â€” Near USB-C connector\n     VINâ†’VBUS, BATâ†’BAT+, GNDâ†’GND\n     PROGâ†’2kÎ©â†’GND (500mA charge)\n     CHRGâ†’1kÎ©â†’LED_REDâ†’GND\n     STDBYâ†’1kÎ©â†’LED_GRNâ†’GND\n\nU3: AP2112K-3.3 (SOT-23-5) â€” Between battery and ESP32\n     VINâ†’switched BAT+, VOUTâ†’3V3, GNDâ†’GND\n     CEâ†’VIN (always enabled)\n\nU4: USBLC6-2SC6 (SOT-23-6) â€” Next to USB-C\n     IO1â†’USB_DP, IO2â†’USB_DN, VBUSâ†’VBUS, GNDâ†’GND\n\nJ1: USB-C Receptacle â€” Board edge (aligned with base port)\n     VBUS, D+â†’USB_DP, D-â†’USB_DN, GND\n     CC1â†’5.1kÎ©â†’GND, CC2â†’5.1kÎ©â†’GND\n\nJ2: JST-PH 2-pin â€” Battery connector\n     Pin1â†’BAT+, Pin2â†’GND\n\nJ3: FPC 6-pin 0.5mm â€” Center of board (cable goes up)\n     Pin1â†’3V3, Pin2â†’GND\n     Pin3â†’BTN_LEFT, Pin4â†’BTN_RIGHT\n     Pin5â†’BTN_BACK, Pin6â†’BTN_FWD\n\nJ4: 5-pin header â€” Center (joystick module)\n     Pin1â†’3V3, Pin2â†’GND\n     Pin3â†’JOY_X, Pin4â†’JOY_Y, Pin5â†’JOY_SW\n\nSW1: Slide switch (SPDT) â€” Board edge\n     COMâ†’BAT+, NOâ†’VIN_SWITCHED\n\nSW2: Tactile (BOOT) â€” Near ESP32\n     GPIO0â†’GND when pressed\n\nSW3: Tactile (RESET) â€” Near ESP32\n     ENâ†’GND when pressed\n\nPull-ups (10kÎ© to 3V3):\n     R_PU1â†’BTN_LEFT, R_PU2â†’BTN_RIGHT\n     R_PU3â†’BTN_BACK, R_PU4â†’BTN_FWD\n     R_PU5â†’JOY_SW\n\nBattery voltage divider:\n     BAT+â†’R5(100kÎ©)â†’VBAT_SENSEâ†’R6(100kÎ©)â†’GND\n\nDecoupling:\n     C1-C4: 100nF on 3V3 near ESP32 (each side)\n     C5: 10ÂµF bulk on 3V3\n     C6: 10ÂµF on VBUS\n     C7: 10ÂµF on BAT+"
